             was charged on the Coroner's Inquisition (only), with <rs id="t18211024-35-off219" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18211024-35-off219" type="offenceCategory" value="kill"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18211024-35-off219" type="offenceSubcategory" value="manslaughter"></interp>
